{"tid":1536804,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"上個月罷買省左Ｄ錢捐左比星火，想拋磚引玉","createTime":"2019-09-03T17:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T13:39:05.000Z","uid":58883,"like":46,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"0a3f1ae133346cf11028d4f4b3b07ecfd76593d6","tid":1536804,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VC727RM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVC727RM.jpg&h=fe94c34d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發起左罷買行動之後，省埋省埋Ｄ錢捐左比星火，想拋磚引玉，但係得我一個唔夠？<br />\n我打算係facebook發起Challenge，呼籲facebook audience 跟機(有25+ followers，主要係中年有少少錢既和理非)。<br />\n<br />\n我地希望更多人可以嚮應罷買／一齊捐錢幫義士。<br />\n<br />\n如果你地聽日之前捐完，請blur個人資訊pm我地 Byebuyday fb/ig/tg (下面有) ，我會將大家既收據大約星期五一次過放上FB去challenge班和理非。<br />\n向星火捐款途徑:<br />\n滙豐銀行: 048-857585-838 <br />\n戶口全名: The Prime Management Service Ltd.<br />\n自動櫃員機戶口名字顯示: T PR**E M*L T*A T*C <br />\n轉數快ID: 3771623<br />\n佢地FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/sparkalliancehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Fsparkalliancehk&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vmWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=80aabb8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/sparkalliancehk</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8x4XWN0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8x4XWN0.jpg&h=30c16670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷買係星星之火，我相信大家一齊去做會好有效果<br />\n______________________________________<br />\n簽署承諾罷買︰<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ORv5Zw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ORv5Zw&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vmWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=8fa05670\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ORv5Zw</a><br />\nfacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/byebuydayhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Fbyebuydayhk&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vmWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=5b3b9140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/byebuydayhk</a><br />\nInstagram: @byebuydayhk<br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/sunfribyebuyTG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FsunfribyebuyTG&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vmWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=195b5e91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sunfribyebuyTG</a> pm: jjjjjjjj1999<br />\n#日五罷買 #SunFriByeBuy<br />\n#罷買救港 #ByeBuySaveHK<br />\n#全民罷買日 #ByeBuyDayHK"},{"pid":"01037fb89dda06bae4aef29d2c28cea6b3701f95","tid":1536804,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:21:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac454c01b213122b312c8